data.description: Are you looking for an opportunity to live every day like you are on vacation in Central Florida? Dreaming of leisurely pool days in the sunshine, balmy walks at sunset overlooking beautiful water views, and fun times with little ones and furry friends at nearby parks? If so, you are going to LOVE the amazing amenities in the Riverstone neighborhood in Lakeland, Florida! With two community pools, dog park, playground and walking paths, there is to so much to do, practically right in your very own back yard. The best part? You won't have to wait to build, and also will not waste your time (or money!) doing repairs or renovations - as you can move right in to this newly constructed 2022 home, to begin living the good life! Situated on a wonderful corner lot, this attractive home has nice curb appeal with a welcoming porch and landscaping. A spacious and open floor plan with dining room, kitchen and living room serve as the heart of the home, boasting tasteful paint colors, high ceilings, custom built-ins and stylish plank-style flooring. The kitchen has ample storage, with wood cabinetry, island and closet pantry, plus granite countertops, Whirlpool stainless steel appliances, and a breakfast bar. Sliding doors in the living room provide great natural light, as well as access to the covered back porch - just waiting for you to enjoy fresh air and relaxation throughout the year! The primary suite is comprised of a large bedroom, a walk-in closet, and an en-suite bathroom with dual sinks, quartz countertops and a shower. There are two additional bedrooms and a full bathroom with shower/tub on the other side of the home, in addition to an interior laundry room. This home has good storage, and is in excellent condition, with various warranties that will convey at closing. Located between Tampa and Orlando, near The Polk Parkway and I4, this location is convenient for anyone who will be commuting, and is just a short drive from world class resorts, popular theme parks, award winning beaches and MORE!
